column8: In my wellbeing services county I should be able to get non-urgent treatment in primary health care within two weeks
column9: Customer fees for public healthcare should be reduced
column10: It is right that public money is spent to support people's use of private healthcare
column11: One round-the-clock specialist hospital with emergency services will be enough in my wellbeing services county in the future
column12: I am prepared to compromise on the social and health services of my home municipality if it is in the interest of the entire wellbeing services county
column13: My wellbeing services county should attract doctors to health centers with financial incentives even if that means cutting spending elsewhere
column14: My wellbeing services county should attract care staff from abroad
column15: My wellbeing services county must ensure that caregivers have a good command of Finnish or Swedish
column16: My wellbeing services county should also offer undocumented people healthcare that is not required by law
column17: This wellbeing services county should stop providing free contraception for young people
column18: My wellbeing services county should train social and healthcare workers about the diversity of sexual orientation and gender
column19: It is right that even small hospitals in Swedish-speaking areas be allowed maintain 24-hour special medical care services due to linguistic rights
column20: Young people should be able to access mental health services without an appointment in my wellbeing services county
column21: We should add more beds to 24-hour service housing for the elderly even if it costs more
column22: In eldercare home visits can be replaced by remote services
column23: Adult children should take more responsibility for caring for their elderly parents than they do now
column24: We must accept that one's place of residence affects the availability of basic social and healthcare services
column25: This wellbeing services county should reduce its purchase of child protection services from large companies
column26: Drug users should have the opportunity to exchange dirty needles for clean ones in all the municipalities in my wellbeing services county
column27: The current fire brigades must be maintained even in remote areas
column28: Wellbeing services counties should be given the right to collect tax
column29: The number of wellbeing services counties should be reduced from the current 21
column30: Well-being areas must make budget cuts within the required timeframe even if that means that services must be quickly reduced
column31: No-one should be allowed to hold triple roles as MP municipal councillor and regional councillor at the same time
column32: My wellbeing services county must take into account the reduction of climate emissions in all its decisions
